Showing the total number and the number of unread messages directly in the
 folder tree
\layout Itemize

New so-called unattended, or away, mode in which all new mail notifications
 and any interactive dialogs are temporarily suppressed
\layout Itemize

A few new commands such as "Clear folder" to delete all messages in a folder
 without even opening it (handy for emptying the trash folder) and "Close"
 and "Close all" folder(s).
\layout Standard

There are several more minor improvements as well:
\layout Itemize

