This dialog allows you to set up or edit an individual filtering rule, it
 contains of the following components:
\layout Itemize

The rule name, in the text entry field at the very top.
 This name is only to help you remember what the rule does and will appear
 in the list of rules in the main Filters Dialog, but is without any further
 significance.
\layout Itemize

Underneath the name, you find the text 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset 

If Message...
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset 

