y negating them by ticking the [Not] box.
 The following conditions can be tested for at present:
\layout Itemize

Always - this rule will always be executed
\layout Itemize

Contains - check if the text next to it is contained in the message component
 selected
\layout Itemize

Match - check if the message component selected is exactly this text (case
 independent)
\layout Itemize

Match Case - check if the message compent selected is exactly this text
